&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Considering that the previous statement inserted one doc into the same url. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;However I wanted to ensure that others are able to confirm if this much is passing&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I see the tests failing when the test is the last one to run , and passing when I moved to the top. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m wondering , how do the no:of JVMs affect the testitself&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
